channel.title: Does anyone to join us in codecloud?
channel.description:
CodeCloud is a platform for collaboratively developing and learning to create innovative products. Each fleet (group) needs 9 members so we need 3 more people before we can start learn by doing.
Do you want to join us? Use the URL codecloud.me followed by /invite/?pId=9&fId=10 (unfortunately new users cannot post links)
Kind regards
